Global Flight Catering Truck Market Insights
Flight Catering Truck Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.7 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Flight Catering Truck Market Overview
The global flight catering truck market size was valued at approximately USD 5.1 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 6.4% from 2024 to 2031. Flight catering trucks are specialized vehicles used to deliver food and beverages to airlines during flights. The increasing demand for air travel, rising disposable income, and growing need for in-flight services are major factors driving market growth. In addition, the increasing adoption of automation in food delivery and logistics within the aviation industry is contributing to the expansion of the market. Furthermore, the growing number of airports and aircraft globally is expected to create substantial opportunities for market players.

